### List hire assets
GET http://localhost:3100/api/hire/assets
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: request-manager

### Create hire asset
POST http://localhost:3100/api/hire/assets
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: request-manager

{
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "assetTag": "HIRE-001",
  "displayName": "Demo gravel hire bike",
  "notes": "Workshop-ready frame"
}

### List hire bookings
GET http://localhost:3100/api/hire/bookings
X-Staff-Role: MANAGER
X-Staff-Id: request-manager

### Create hire booking
POST http://localhost:3100/api/hire/bookings
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: request-staff

{
  "hireAssetId": "{{hireAssetId}}",
  "customerId": "{{customerId}}",
  "startsAt": "2026-03-13T09:00:00.000Z",
  "dueBackAt": "2026-03-14T17:00:00.000Z",
  "hirePricePence": 4500,
  "depositPence": 15000,
  "notes": "Passport checked"
}

### Checkout hire booking
POST http://localhost:3100/api/hire/bookings/{{hireBookingId}}/checkout
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: request-staff

{
  "depositHeldPence": 15000
}

### Return hire booking
POST http://localhost:3100/api/hire/bookings/{{hireBookingId}}/return
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: request-staff

{
  "depositOutcome": "RETURNED"
}

### Cancel reserved hire booking
POST http://localhost:3100/api/hire/bookings/{{hireBookingId}}/cancel
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: request-staff
